text: President Trump revealed early Friday morning that he and the first lady, Melania Trump, had tested positive for the coronavirus. It is not clear when or how Mr. Trump contracted the virus. But over the past week, he interacted with scores of staff members, donors and supporters. Photographers for The New York Times captured some of those meetings.
snippet: President Trump revealed early Friday  that he had tested positive for coronavirus. Over the past week, he interacted with scores of staff members, donors and supporters.
